---

<PageLayout
  title="Los Cabos Wedding Photographer | Cabo Image by Miguel Ventura"
  description="Award-winning wedding and portrait photographer based in Los Cabos, Mexico. Serving Cabo San Lucas, San José del Cabo, and destination weddings throughout Baja California Sur."
  headerTransparent={true}
>

  <!--
    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║   HOMEPAGE — DESIGN IN PROGRESS                                  ║
    ║   Section order:                                                 ║
    ║   1. Hero (full-screen image + headline)                         ║
    ║   2. Featured Work (6–9 best images, masonry or grid)            ║
    ║   3. Services Overview (7 service cards)                         ║
    ║   4. About Snippet (Miguel + photo + link)                       ║
    ║   5. Testimonials Carousel                                       ║
    ║   6. Instagram Feed (latest 6–9 posts)                           ║
    ║   7. Final CTA (book a consultation)                             ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
  -->

  <!-- TEMPORARY PLACEHOLDER -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="text-center px-6">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Coming Soon</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display-lg text-cabo-white mb-6">
        Cabo Image
      </h1>
      <p class="font-serif text-xl text-cabo-muted italic mb-2">
        by Miguel Ventura
      </p>
      <p class="text-cabo-subtle font-sans text-sm tracking-wider mb-10">
        Wedding &amp; Lifestyle Photographer · Los Cabos, Mexico
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 border border-cabo-gold text-cabo-gold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans hover:bg-cabo-gold hover:text-cabo-black transition-all duration-300"
      >
        Book a Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
